:::Ramjet:::

Ramjet: Well, me and my team members are the same bots as the Decepticons 
whose names we have.  The three of us were banished from Cybertron for... 
treachery... and we came here after a brief stint in the Alliance, we joined 
up with the Destrons.  We saw many leaders pass.  Magmatron, Bobertron, 
Cerberus, Shredder, and Magmatron again.  We endured countless hardships and 
right when things were getting better for us, Magmatron left. That was when i 
met the rest of you and that leads up to now.

--part1_ce.12a04fa1.27f2b00d_boundary
